snippet.title: VEGANGSTERS DEMO OUT NOW | Official Announcement Trailer 🃏🥔
snippet.description:
Try the demo and add it to your #Wishlist on Steam! 🥔

🔹https://store.steampowered.com/app/2449390/Vegangsters/

Make your way through this deckbuilder roguelike with real-time mechanics, and save the city from the Vegangsters! Fight against the worst criminals in a series of turn-based combats determined by the speed of your cards.
